  <datafield tag="245" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">The Holistic structure of causal quantum theory, its implementation in the Einstein-Jordan conundrum and its violation in more recent particle theories</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="246" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">The holistic structure of causal quantum theory, its implementation in the Einstein-Jordan conundrum and its violation in more recent particle theories</subfield>
